{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":502,"text":"Frugal Digital is essentially a small research group at C.I.D."},{"time":5787,"text":"where we are looking to find"},{"time":7930,"text":"alternate visions of how to create a digitally inclusive society."},{"time":12470,"text":"That's what we're after."},{"time":14278,"text":"And we do this because we actually believe"},{"time":16458,"text":"that silicon technology today is mostly about"},{"time":19732,"text":"a culture of excess."},{"time":21484,"text":"It's about the fastest and the most efficient"},{"time":23657,"text":"and the most dazzling gadget you can have,"},{"time":26087,"text":"while about two-thirds of the world"},{"time":28985,"text":"can hardly reach the most basic of this technology"},{"time":32669,"text":"to even address fundamental needs in life,"},{"time":36252,"text":"including health care, education"},{"time":38420,"text":"and all these kinds of very fundamental issues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42499,"text":"So before I start, I want to talk about a little anecdote,"},{"time":45744,"text":"a little story about a man I met once in Mumbai."},{"time":49767,"text":"So this man, his name is Sathi Shri."},{"time":51954,"text":"He is an outstanding person,"},{"time":54060,"text":"because he's a small entrepreneur."},{"time":56202,"text":"He runs a little shop"},{"time":57944,"text":"in one of the back streets of Mumbai."},{"time":59947,"text":"He has this little 10-square-meter store,"},{"time":62995,"text":"where so much is being done."},{"time":65145,"text":"It's incredible, because I couldn't believe my eyes"},{"time":67050,"text":"when I once just happened to bump into him."},{"time":69533,"text":"Basically, what he does is, he has all these services"},{"time":71658,"text":"for micro-payments and booking tickets"},{"time":74411,"text":"and all kinds of basic things that you would go online for,"},{"time":77744,"text":"but he does it for people offline"},{"time":79933,"text":"and connects to the digital world."},{"time":81930,"text":"More importantly, he makes his money"},{"time":83435,"text":"by selling these mobile recharge coupons, you know,"},{"time":86028,"text":"for the prepaid subscriptions."},{"time":88303,"text":"But then, in the backside, he's got this little nook"},{"time":91544,"text":"with a few of his employees"},{"time":94117,"text":"where they can fix almost anything."},{"time":96701,"text":"Any cell phone, any gadget you can bring them, they can fix it."},{"time":99959,"text":"And it's pretty incredible because I took my iPhone there,"},{"time":103077,"text":"and he was like, \"Yeah, do you want an upgrade?\""},{"time":105246,"text":"\"Yes.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":107564,"text":"I was a bit skeptical, but then, I decided"},{"time":109504,"text":"to give him a Nokia instead. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":114137,"text":"But what I was amazed about is this reverse engineering"},{"time":119352,"text":"and know-how that's built into this little two meters of space."},{"time":124304,"text":"They have figured out everything that's required"},{"time":126895,"text":"to dismantle, take things apart,"},{"time":128921,"text":"rewrite the circuitry, re-flash the firmware,"},{"time":131880,"text":"do whatever you want to with the phone,"},{"time":133847,"text":"and they can fix anything so quickly."},{"time":136416,"text":"You can hand over a phone this morning"},{"time":138416,"text":"and you can go pick it up after lunch,"},{"time":140336,"text":"and it was quite incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142256,"text":"But then we were wondering whether this is"},{"time":143827,"text":"a local phenomenon, or is truly global?"},{"time":146369,"text":"And, over time, we started understanding"},{"time":148619,"text":"and systematically researching"},{"time":150338,"text":"what this tinkering ecosystem is about,"},{"time":152454,"text":"because that is something that's happening"},{"time":154059,"text":"not just in one street corner in Mumbai."},{"time":156091,"text":"It's actually happening in all parts of the country."},{"time":159205,"text":"It's even happening in Africa, like, for example,"},{"time":161466,"text":"in Cape Town we did extensive research on this."},{"time":163513,"text":"Even here in Doha I found this little nook"},{"time":166708,"text":"where you can get alarm clocks and watches fixed,"},{"time":169595,"text":"and it's a lot of tiny little parts. It's not easy."},{"time":172796,"text":"You've got to try it on your own to believe it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174909,"text":"But what fuels this?"},{"time":176463,"text":"It's this entire ecosystem of low-cost parts"},{"time":179971,"text":"and supplies that are produced all over the world, literally,"},{"time":183277,"text":"and then redistributed to basically service this industry,"},{"time":187043,"text":"and you can even buy salvaged parts."},{"time":189214,"text":"Basically, you don't have to necessarily buy"},{"time":191370,"text":"brand new things. You have condemned computers"},{"time":193833,"text":"that are stripped apart,"},{"time":195140,"text":"and you can buy salvaged components"},{"time":196710,"text":"and things that you can reassemble in a new configuration."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200531,"text":"But what does this new, sort of, approach give us?"},{"time":204012,"text":"That's the real question, because this is something"},{"time":205932,"text":"that's been there, part of every society"},{"time":208157,"text":"that's deprived of enough resources."},{"time":210523,"text":"But there's an interesting paradigm."},{"time":212420,"text":"There's the traditional crafts,"},{"time":213912,"text":"and then there's the technology crafts."},{"time":215915,"text":"We call it the technology crafts because these are emerging."},{"time":218123,"text":"They're not something that's been established."},{"time":220195,"text":"It's not something that's institutionalized."},{"time":222862,"text":"It's not taught in universities."},{"time":224633,"text":"It's taught [by] word of mouth,"},{"time":226356,"text":"and it's an informal education system around this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228265,"text":"So we said, \"What can we get out of this?"},{"time":231067,"text":"You know, like, what are the key values that we can get out of this?\""},{"time":233801,"text":"The main thing is a fix-it-locally culture,"},{"time":236146,"text":"which is fantastic because it means that your product"},{"time":238486,"text":"or your service doesn't have to go through"},{"time":240531,"text":"a huge bureaucratic system to get it fixed."},{"time":243139,"text":"It also affords us cheap fabrication, which is fantastic,"},{"time":246218,"text":"so it means that you can do a lot more with it."},{"time":248250,"text":"And then, the most important thing is,"},{"time":250564,"text":"it gives us large math for low cost."},{"time":252940,"text":"So it means that you can actually embed"},{"time":255269,"text":"pretty clever algorithms and lots of other kinds"},{"time":258794,"text":"of extendable ideas into really simple devices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262452,"text":"So, what we call this is a silicon cottage industry."},{"time":267260,"text":"It's basically what was the system or the paradigm"},{"time":270206,"text":"before the industrial revolution is now re-happening"},{"time":272670,"text":"in a whole new way in small digital shops"},{"time":275678,"text":"across the planet in most developing countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278759,"text":"So, we kind of toyed around with this idea,"},{"time":282893,"text":"and we said, \"What can we do with this?"},{"time":284571,"text":"Can we make a little product or a service out of it?\""},{"time":287099,"text":"So one of the first things we did is this thing called"},{"time":289519,"text":"a multimedia platform. We call it a lunch box."},{"time":291915,"text":"Basically one of the contexts that we studied was"},{"time":294666,"text":"schools in very remote parts of India."},{"time":298153,"text":"So there is this amazing concept called the one-teacher school,"},{"time":301412,"text":"which is basically a single teacher who is a multitasker"},{"time":304114,"text":"who teaches this amazing little social setting."},{"time":306591,"text":"It's an informal school,"},{"time":308128,"text":"but it's really about holistic education."},{"time":310287,"text":"The only thing that they don't have"},{"time":311525,"text":"is access to resources. They don't even have a textbook"},{"time":313919,"text":"sometimes, and they don't even have a proper curriculum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316746,"text":"So we said, \"What can we do to empower this teacher"},{"time":320250,"text":"to do more?\" How to access the digital world?"},{"time":323062,"text":"Instead of being the sole guardian of information,"},{"time":325624,"text":"be a facilitator to all this information."},{"time":328028,"text":"So we said, \"What are the steps required to empower the teacher?\""},{"time":331412,"text":"How do you make this teacher into a digital gateway,"},{"time":334067,"text":"and how do you design an inexpensive multimedia platform"},{"time":336599,"text":"that can be constructed locally and serviced locally?\""},{"time":339591,"text":"So we walked around."},{"time":341934,"text":"We went and scavenged the nearby markets,"},{"time":344224,"text":"and we tried to understand, \"What can we pick up that will make this happen?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":348245,"text":"So the thing that we got"},{"time":350772,"text":"was a little mobile phone with a little pico projector"},{"time":353979,"text":"that comes for about 60 dollars."},{"time":356316,"text":"We went a bought a flashlight with a very big battery,"},{"time":358772,"text":"and a bunch of small speakers."},{"time":360562,"text":"So essentially, the mobile phone gives us"},{"time":362860,"text":"a connected multimedia platform."},{"time":364784,"text":"It allows us to get online and allows us to load up files"},{"time":368269,"text":"of different formats and play them."},{"time":370620,"text":"The flashlight gives us this really intense, bright L.E.D.,"},{"time":373646,"text":"and six hours worth of rechargeable battery pack,"},{"time":376637,"text":"and the lunch box is a nice little package"},{"time":378853,"text":"in which you can put everything inside,"},{"time":380900,"text":"and a bunch of mini speakers to sort of"},{"time":382463,"text":"amplify the sound large enough."},{"time":383881,"text":"Believe me, those little classrooms are really noisy."},{"time":387420,"text":"They are kids who scream at the top of their voices,"},{"time":390013,"text":"and you really have to get above that."},{"time":391673,"text":"And we took it back to this little tinkering setup"},{"time":394394,"text":"of a mobile phone repair shop,"},{"time":396484,"text":"and then the magic happens."},{"time":397912,"text":"We dismantle the whole thing,"},{"time":399293,"text":"we reassemble it in a new configuration,"},{"time":401650,"text":"and we do this hardware mashup,"},{"time":403828,"text":"systematically training the guy how to do this."},{"time":406437,"text":"Out comes this, a little lunch box -- form factor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409892,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":416718,"text":"And we systematically field tested,"},{"time":419736,"text":"because in the field testing we learned some"},{"time":422104,"text":"important lessons, and we went through many iterations."},{"time":424621,"text":"One of the key issues was battery consumption and charging."},{"time":427316,"text":"Luminosity was an issue, when you have too much bright sunlight outside."},{"time":431294,"text":"Often the roofs are broken, so you don't have enough"},{"time":433846,"text":"darkness in the classroom to do these things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436974,"text":"We extended this idea. We tested it many times over,"},{"time":439816,"text":"and the next version we came up with was a box"},{"time":442394,"text":"that kind of could trickle charge on solar energy,"},{"time":444774,"text":"but most importantly connect to a car battery,"},{"time":447573,"text":"because a car battery is a ubiquitous source of power"},{"time":450567,"text":"in places where there's not enough electricity"},{"time":452774,"text":"or erratic electricity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454734,"text":"And the other key thing that we did was"},{"time":456703,"text":"make this box run off a USB key, because we realized"},{"time":459165,"text":"that even though there was GPRS and all that on paper,"},{"time":462519,"text":"at least, in theory, it was much more efficient"},{"time":465094,"text":"to send the data on a little USB key by surface mail."},{"time":468984,"text":"It might take a few days to get there,"},{"time":470824,"text":"but at least it gets there in high definition"},{"time":473198,"text":"and in a reliable quality."},{"time":475413,"text":"So we made this box, and we tested it again"},{"time":477695,"text":"and again and again, and we're going through"},{"time":479230,"text":"multiple iterations to do these things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480779,"text":"But it's not limited to just education."},{"time":483748,"text":"This kind of a technique or metrology"},{"time":485614,"text":"can actually be applied to other kinds of areas,"},{"time":487626,"text":"and I'm going to tell you one more little story."},{"time":489534,"text":"It's about this little device called a medi-meter."},{"time":491989,"text":"It's basically a little health care screening tool that we developed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495356,"text":"In India, there is a context of these amazing people,"},{"time":498683,"text":"the health care workers called ASHA workers."},{"time":500962,"text":"They are essentially foot soldiers for the health care system"},{"time":503379,"text":"who live in the local community and are trained"},{"time":505763,"text":"with basic tools and basic concepts of health care,"},{"time":508331,"text":"and the main purpose is basically to inform people"},{"time":512093,"text":"to basically, how to lead a better life, but also"},{"time":515626,"text":"to divert or sort of make recommendations"},{"time":518854,"text":"of what kind of health care should they approach?"},{"time":521528,"text":"They are basically referral services, essentially."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524240,"text":"But the problem with that is that we realized"},{"time":526548,"text":"after a bunch of research that they are amazing"},{"time":530738,"text":"at referring people to the nearest clinic"},{"time":533218,"text":"or the public health care system, but what happens at the"},{"time":536091,"text":"public health care system is this: these incredibly long lines"},{"time":540169,"text":"and too many people who overload the system"},{"time":542979,"text":"simply because there's not enough doctors and facilities"},{"time":545545,"text":"for the population that's being referred."},{"time":547747,"text":"So everything from a common cold"},{"time":549866,"text":"to a serious case of malaria gets almost the same"},{"time":552526,"text":"level of attention, and there's no priorities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555570,"text":"So we said, \"Come on, there's got to be a better way"},{"time":557641,"text":"of doing this for sure.\""},{"time":559442,"text":"So we said, \"What can we do with the ASHA worker"},{"time":562019,"text":"that'll allow this ASHA worker to become an interesting filter,"},{"time":565950,"text":"but not just a filter, a really well thought through referral"},{"time":568465,"text":"system that allows load balancing of the network,"},{"time":571946,"text":"and directs patients to different sources of health care"},{"time":575885,"text":"based on the severity or the criticalness of those situations?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":579765,"text":"So the real key question was,"},{"time":581746,"text":"how do we empower this woman?"},{"time":583414,"text":"How do we empower her with simple tools"},{"time":585341,"text":"that's not diagnostic but more screening in nature"},{"time":588292,"text":"so she at least knows how to advise the patients better?"},{"time":592072,"text":"And that'll make such a huge difference on the system,"},{"time":594100,"text":"because the amount of waiting time and the amount of"},{"time":599018,"text":"distances that people need to travel, often sometimes"},{"time":600938,"text":"seven to 15 kilometers, sometimes by foot,"},{"time":603611,"text":"to get a simple health check done, is very, very detrimental"},{"time":609074,"text":"in the sense that it really dissuades people"},{"time":611528,"text":"from getting access to health care."},{"time":613537,"text":"So if there was something that she could do,"},{"time":615572,"text":"that would be amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616681,"text":"So what we did was that we converted this device"},{"time":619742,"text":"into a medical device."},{"time":621559,"text":"I want to demo this actually,"},{"time":622835,"text":"because it's a very simple process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625508,"text":"Bruno, do you want to join us? (Cheers)"},{"time":627917,"text":"Come along. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":634119,"text":"So, what we're going to do is that"},{"time":637044,"text":"we're going to measure a few basic parameters on you,"},{"time":640016,"text":"including your pulse rate and the amount of oxygen"},{"time":642871,"text":"that's there in your blood."},{"time":644744,"text":"So you're going to put your thumb on top of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648035,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Like this, works?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649809,"text":"Vinay Venkatraman: Yeah. That's right. BG: Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651475,"text":"VV: So I'm going to start it up. I hope it works."},{"time":655483,"text":"(Beeps) It even beeps, because it's an alarm clock, after all."},{"time":659833,"text":"So ... (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":661845,"text":"So I take it into the start position, and then"},{"time":666236,"text":"I press the read button. (Beeps)"},{"time":669848,"text":"So it's taking a little reading from you. (Beeps)"},{"time":675329,"text":"And then the pointer goes and points to three different options."},{"time":678107,"text":"Let's see what happens here."},{"time":681382,"text":"(Beeps) Oh Bruno, you can go home, actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683465,"text":"BG: Great. Good news. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":687301,"text":"VV: So ... (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":689646,"text":"So the thing about this is that"},{"time":692863,"text":"if the pointer, unfortunately, had pointed to the red spot,"},{"time":696968,"text":"we would have to rush you to a hospital."},{"time":698814,"text":"Luckily, not today. And if it had pointed to the orange"},{"time":702934,"text":"or the amber, it basically meant you had to have,"},{"time":705763,"text":"sort of, more continuous care from the health care worker."},{"time":708807,"text":"So that was a very simple three-step screening process"},{"time":711158,"text":"that could basically change the equation"},{"time":713273,"text":"of how public health care works in so many different ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716013,"text":"BG: Thank you for the good news. VV: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717910,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":722303,"text":"So, very briefly, I'll just explain to you how this is done,"},{"time":725743,"text":"because that's the more interesting part."},{"time":728033,"text":"So essentially, the three things that are required"},{"time":730727,"text":"to make this conversion from this guy to this guy"},{"time":735255,"text":"is a cheap remote control for a television"},{"time":739384,"text":"that you can almost find in every home today,"},{"time":742295,"text":"some parts from a computer mouse, basically,"},{"time":746009,"text":"something that you can scavenge for very low cost,"},{"time":749872,"text":"and a few parts that have to be pre-programmed."},{"time":752783,"text":"Basically this is a micro-controller with a few"},{"time":755184,"text":"extra components that can be shipped for very little cost"},{"time":757979,"text":"across the world, and that's what is all required"},{"time":760972,"text":"with a little bit of local tinkering talent"},{"time":763363,"text":"to convert the device into something else."},{"time":766150,"text":"So we are right now doing some systematic field tests"},{"time":769546,"text":"to basically ascertain whether something like this actually"},{"time":772596,"text":"makes sense to the ASHA worker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774163,"text":"We are going through some reference tests to compare it"},{"time":777707,"text":"against professional equipment to see if there's a degree"},{"time":781165,"text":"of change in efficacy and if it actually makes an impact"},{"time":783487,"text":"in people's lives. But most importantly,"},{"time":786095,"text":"what we are trying to do right now"},{"time":787890,"text":"is we are trying to scale this up, because there"},{"time":790144,"text":"are over 250,000 ASHA workers on the ground"},{"time":792831,"text":"who are these amazing foot soldiers, and if we can"},{"time":795568,"text":"give at least a fraction of them the access to these things,"},{"time":799128,"text":"it just changes the way the economics of public health care"},{"time":802086,"text":"works, and it changes the way systems actually function,"},{"time":805097,"text":"not just on a systematic planning level,"},{"time":809363,"text":"but also in a very grassroots, bottom-up level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812548,"text":"So that's it, and we hope to do this in a big way."},{"time":815349,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":818507,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}